description: Evading the jaws of a monstrous stone dog, Grey heads to an abandoned coal mine filled with a horde of zombies!
name: Lost and Gone Forever

volume.name: Sir Edward Grey, Witchfinder: Lost and Gone Forever

description: The diminutive versions of the Endless from Neil Gaiman's SANDMAN mythos are back by popular demand in DELIRIUM'S PARTY: A LITTLE ENDLESS STORYBOOK. In an effort to rid Despair of her unhappiness once and for all, Little Delirium throws a party for her dour sister and invites siblings Dream, Destruction, Death, Destiny and Desire. But this is no ordinary affair. We're talking about a party planner who is the personification of delirium, so you can only imagine that this event will be as outrageous and unpredictable as Little Delirium's haircolor. But whether Delirium's party will be a smashing success – or whether it will end in tears – is anyone's guess. Brought to life through whimsical prose and watercolor by multiple award-winner Jill Thompson, DELIRIUM'S PARTY: A LITTLE ENDLESS STORYBOOK will be an affair to remember for all time – and all ages.
name: HC

volume.name: Delirium's Party: A Little Endless Storybook

description: This issue marks the beginning of the new story "5 Brains, 5 Months," which will play out in "real time" over the course of the coming issues. In May, 2011, zombie girl Gwen and her friends solve a mystery just in time to keep an even more mysterious appointment with Amon, the sexy mummy, while the vampire girls add a new member to their number and the monster hunters prowl the streets. And in the first of a series of backup stories, we meet a group of government agents who will soon be making life very difficult for Gwen and company. But who are the Dead Presidents?
name: Arrivals and Exits: Part One of Six Feet Under and Rising

description: The most powerful super team ever—that’s right, we said it—faces the threat of the infamous Dire Wraiths! But can a squad that includes Silver Surfer, Gladiator and Beta-Ray Bill defeat this diabolical race and the dark magic they are unleashing? Meanwhile, Rocket Raccoon and Groot zoom deeper into their adventure as Rocket’s secret and slightly crazy origin is revealed!
name: Wraithfire

concept_credits.name: Rocket Raccoon & Groot Themed Variant Cover

first_appearance_concepts.name: Rocket Raccoon & Groot Themed Variant Cover

description:
Catman's past crawls back to haunt him when three men kidnap his long-lost son. His Secret Six teammates come to his aid, leaving a bloody trail of vengeance behind them. Will they be too late to save the only person Catman cares about? Find out in these stories from SECRET SIX #25-29 and ACTION COMICS #897!

The Secret Six is divided into two opposing teams sent to battle each other in the land of Skataris. Waiting for them back home is Lex Luthor, the creator of the team, who has a job for them.
name: TPB

description: The next chapter in this exciting tale of the Red Scorpion Gang! When the bunny bodyguard Usagi discovers the body of a magistrate’s kidnapped son, a bloody showdown with the Red Scorpions ensues. How will the lone samurai--a noble follower of bushido--fare against this gang of unscrupulous crooks?
name: Those Who Tread on the Scorpion's Tail, Part 2

description: While Broom banishes a ghost from a priest’s home, Liz explores the woods around the house, where a terrible witch hunt occurred and a woman was murdered! Also--the accident in which Liz killed her family is finally revealed in detail!
name: 2 (of 3)

first_appearance_teams.name: Bureau for Paranormal Research and Defense

team_credits.name: Bureau for Paranormal Research and Defense

description: In the aftermath of VAC's first superhero combat trial, Greg Mallory finds himself cast adrift- until the opportunity for vengeance suddenly presents itself. A clandestine organization arises with the coming of the cold war, and Mallory finds himself playing spymaster... with no inkling of the moral compromise he'll eventually be forced to make. Sixty years of the Boys' secret history continues, in part three of Barbary Coast.
name: Barbary Coast, Part Three

description: Carving a bloody swath through Dracula's forces, facing down the Lord of the Vampires himself, Vampirella is now face to face with an ancient, unknowable evil, a terrifying force that plans to make Vampirella its eternal queen.
name: Crown of Worms, Part 5: Dead Reckoning

description: A new adventure begins! Following the deadly events in Shem, Red Sonja makes her way to Koth -- and a family dispute between rival princes, all keen to seize the throne. And amid the intrigue and the skullduggery, assassins lurk: enemies, loyal to an old adversary that will stop at nothing until the She-Devil with a Sword is dead.

description: Superman must exile himself from Earth after he contracts a lethal virus, and searches for the cure. But Lobo wants that cure, too.
name: Superman vs Lobo Misery in Space!

description: Bones will be broken and heads will roll! The Goon is a laugh-out-loud, action-packed romp through the streets of a town infested with zombies. An insane priest is building himself an army of the undead, and there's only one man who can put them in their place: the man they call Goon.
name: Volume 1

volume.name: Ice Age on the World of Magic: The Gathering

description: The OFFICIAL comics prequel to the Marvel Studios summer blockbuster begins here! As Captain America, Steve Rogers is the inspiration for millions during the dark days of World War Two -- but where did he get his inspiration from? How did he meet his best friend, 'Bucky' Barnes? And what set him on the path to becoming the First Avenger? New York Times bestselling writer Fred Van Lente (AMAZING SPIDER-MAN) and star artists Luke Ross (CAPTAIN AMERICA) and Neil Edwards (FANTASTIC FOUR) take you on an all-new adventure to the European battlefields before the movie hits theaters!
name: Captain America: First Vengeance, Part 1

description: The Goon and Franky have been best friends ever since they was tykes. Find out how the two little ankle-biters became best pals, and how they muscled their way into the rackets of big-time crime-boss, Labrazio - who, incidentally, nobody's seen in a while. This trip down memory lane ain't gonna be no joyride, neither. Franky and the Goon are going to have to take on a horde of zombies, an army of hoboes, a couple of grave robbin' mongoloids, a guy with a gold head and his killer robot, a pie-crazed skunk ape, one homely, man-crazy sea hag, and whole lot of other things that smell just as bad if not worse. Pick up a copy, because those uptown rich people may have the cops and their G-men, but down here all we got is the Goon!
name: Volume 2

volume.name: The Goon: My Murderous Childhood (and other Grievous Yarns)

description: Hartmann takes a road trip to Chicago to visit a former WFW superstar - only he walks right into the middle of an independent wrestling turf war! Will he be caught in the crossfire? Featuring a special guest appearance by TNA superstar Shawn Daivari (Sheik Abdul Bashir)! The mini-series event concludes here!
The tryout continues! Does Hartmann have what it takes to get into Leo London's wrestling school or will the experience leave him broken both in spirit and body?
